This branch is dedicated to:

1) Adding data to track a user's last authentication
2) If a user has authenticated within a time limit, do not prompt them to login again
3) If a user has not authenticated within a time limit, ask for only a password and assume the username
4) Allow a user to deauthenticate, track authentication state
5) If no settings file is found, require both username and password
6) Allow user to delete settings file